      "content": "it just feels like there's no version of the future where this goes away. i look at the empty space where his bed used to be and i just... i don't want to be here for the silence anymore. you said about having the courage to set it down... does that mean it's okay to just give up? like, is giving up actually an option when it's this much pain?",
